        "We leveraged **NOAA‚Äôs GSOD** dataset (2018‚Äì2024) hosted on BigQuery as the foundation for our analysis. The exploration phase began by examining dataset scale‚Äîcounting the total rows and inspecting the last ten records‚Äîto confirm consistency and completeness. We then extracted metadata, including overall shape, column count, and variable names, to build a clear understanding of the dataset‚Äôs structure before moving into preprocessing and modeling.\n",
